General.Name: Rey Resources Ltd
General.Description: Rey Resources Limited engages in exploring for and developing energy resources in Western Australia. The company holds a 100% interest in the Derby Block EP487; and a 20% interest in the Canning Basin petroleum permits EP457 and EP458 (Fitzroy Blocks). It also holds a 100% interest in the Lennard Shelf Blocks, which comprises a petroleum exploration license EP104, a retention license R1, and one production license L15 in the Canning Basin. In addition, the company holds 100% interests in the Duchess Paradise Coal Project located in the Canning Basin. Further, it holds 20% interest in 7 conventional gas production licenses in Surat Gas Project located in Surat Basin, Queensland. The company was incorporated in 2004 and is based in Sydney, Australia.
